data.description: As you approach the property, the corner lot location provides a sense of space and privacy. The exterior features a newly replaced roof. The  well-maintained landscaping adds to the curb appeal, creating a welcoming first impression. The open layout of the house seamlessly connects the living spaces, promoting a sense of togetherness while allowing for various design possibilities. The updated plumbing ensures reliable functionality  throughout the home, providing peace of mind for years to come. The three bedrooms offer comfortable retreats, each featuring its own unique charm.  The master bedroom, complete with an en-suite bathroom, provides a private sanctuary for relaxation. The additional two bedrooms are well-proportioned and ideal for family members or guests. Step inside to discover a sunroom that bathes the interior in natural light, creating a serene and inviting atmosphere. This versatile space could be used as a cozy reading nook, a home office, or simply a tranquil area to enjoy. One of the standout features of this property is the full basement. With its generous space, it presents opportunities for a multitude of uses. Whether you envision a game room, a home theater, or an expansive storage area, the basement is a blank canvas awaiting your creative touch. Seller is offering $5,000 towards closing and $3,000 lender credit when using preferred lender, Jose Plascencia with Cardinal Financial.
